des: Crossfit Felix is a Crossfit gym in the Belltown neighborhood of Seattle that will help you reach your fitness goals. With this skill you can learn about the workouts for the day or hear any announcements on your Alexa enabled device.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
